    id: slugger
    displayName: Slugger
    pseudo: Slugger
    fullName: Alex Reynolds
    description: 'Alex Reynolds, known as Slugger, was a rising star in baseball celebrated for his powerful batting. During a crucial game under a starlit sky, stardust infused him with superhuman strength and agility. Now wielding a stardust-charged bat, Slugger defends humanity from Underworld threats with resilience and heroism.'
