    description: 'Sarah Thompson, also known as Ace, was a celebrated professional baseball player known for her powerful batting and strategic leadership. Exposure to stardust enhanced her abilities, granting superhuman strength and agility. Embracing her new powers, Ace wields a stardust-charged baseball bat against Underworld threats, driven by her passion for sportsmanship and determination to protect humanity.'
